4.html| archivedate= January 30, 2009 | url-status= live}}</ref><ref name=\"Japansales3\">{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5123288/last-year-japanese-game-market-experienced-shrinkage |title=Last Year, Japanese Game Market Experienced Shrinkage |author=Brian Ashcraft |publisher=Kotaku |date=January 5, 2009 |accessdate=January 14, 2009| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090122045647/http://kotaku.com/5123288/last-year-japanese-game-market-experienced-shrinkage| archivedate= January 22, 2009 | url-status= live}}</ref>\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Place\n!Console\n!Units sold\n|-\n|1\n|[[Nintendo DS]]\n|align=right|4,029,804\n|-\n|2\n|[[PlayStation Portable]]\n|align=right|3,543,171\n|-\n|3\n|[[Wii]]\n|align=right|2,908,342\n|-\n|4\n|[[PlayStation 3]]\n|align=right|991,303\n|-\n|5\n|[[PlayStation 2]]\n|align=right|480,664\n|-\n|6\n|[[Xbox 360]]\n|align=right|317,859\n|-\n|7\n|Other\n|align=right|9,575\n|}\n\n'''Best-selling video games of 2008 in Japan (December 31, 2007 \u2013 December 28, 2008)'''<ref name=Japansales/><ref name=Japansales2/><ref name=Japansales3/>\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Place\n!Title\n!Platform\n!Publisher\n!Units sold\n|-\n|1\n|''[[Monster Hunter Portable 2nd G]]''\n|[[PlayStation Portable|PSP]]\n|[[Capcom]]\n|align=right|2,452,111\n|-\n|2\n|''[[Pok\u00e9mon Platinum]]''\n|[[Nintendo DS|NDS]]\n|[[The Pok\u00e9mon Company|Pok\u00e9mon Company]]\n|align=right|2,187,337\n|-\n|3\n|''[[Wii Fit]]''\n|[[Wii]]\n|[[Nintendo]]\n|align=right|2,149,131\n|-\n|4\n|''[[Mario Kart Wii]]''\n|Wii\n|Nintendo\n|align=right|2,003,315\n|-\n|5\n|''[[Super Smash Bros. Brawl]]''\n|Wii\n|Nintendo\n|align=right|1,747,113\n|-\n|6\n|''[[Rhythm Heaven]]''\n|NDS\n|Nintendo\n|align=right|1,350,671\n|-\n|7\n|''[[Dragon Quest V: Hand of the Heavenly Bride]]''\n|NDS\n|[[Square Enix]]\n|align=right|1,176,082\n|-\n|8\n|''[[Animal Crossing: City Folk]]''\n|Wii\n|Nintendo\n|align=right|895,302\n|-\n|9\n|''[[Kirby Super Star Ultra]]''\n|NDS\n|Nintendo\n|align=right|855,427\